snippet.title: Divided Land - Gameplay Footage (WIP)
snippet.description:
Divided Land is a multiplayer RPG game that features realistic survival mechanics and skill-based melee combat in a vast medieval open world.

Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/NjbgSPP
